{"tid":2268803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓諧星皮膚病惡化 母親遺書不忍女兒痛苦獨自離去","createTime":"2020-11-03T05:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T05:50:27.000Z","uid":330450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1cfeb86d460f264ff97454f3e6a154f7bd63367e","tid":2268803,"uid":330450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"韓國女諧星朴智宣2日被發現與媽媽陳屍在首爾住處，警方在現場發現疑似是朴智宣的母親留下的遺書，內容是提到女兒因為皮膚病惡化而想不開，而她不忍心讓女兒獨自離去。<br />\n<br />\n據「朝鮮日報」報導，警方在現場發現疑似是朴智宣母親寫下的遺書，內容透露著由於女兒罹患皮膚病感到很痛苦，最近因為在治療其他疾病，導致皮膚病惡化，不想讓女兒一個人走，對不起丈夫。而朴智宣在2014年接受訪問時，曾透露自己罹患一種皮膚病，在陽光下曝曬會出現斑疹以及瘙癢的情況，這樣敏感的肌膚，讓她也無法上妝。而她10月23日曾對「體育朝鮮」表示，要進行一個小手術，讓大家不用擔心，之後會專心休養，所以接下來的演藝活動會暫停。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//link <a href=\"https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10088/4984300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstars.udn.com%2Fstar%2Fstory%2F10088%2F4984300&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0Enfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=8e1b4a3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10088/4984300</a>"},{"pid":"77036ef1b129d306fe74f2580cc449cbd0362eff","tid":2268803,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:27:36.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7401ea696f2e5e9f307b2b744dd771d4910b1040","tid":2268803,"uid":330450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:28:25.000Z","msg":"想像下個阿媽開門見到個女死左有幾絕望先會選擇一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4be7bd5cce3d22b0b6f052796be7ca30b7c801","tid":2268803,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50b85e